data.description: 720 square foot detached RV garage (20'x36' per county), and a 1,600 square foot shop (40'x40') with 3 overhead garage doors, 2 RV sized. Shop has concrete floor, it's own electrical panel, and loft storage. Room for your boat, for the car enthusiast, to work on your favorite hobbies,... 3 Bedroom/2 Bath Home on 1/3 acre on a dead-end street, built in 1953, but updated in 1996 with new windows and cement fibre siding. Brand new dishwasher in Kitchen. Feels larger than its 1257 square feet. Conveniently located for freeway access, shopping and restaurants.
